The paper proposes an extension of the BPMN standard for modeling business processes that takes into account case and persistent data. It also discusses verification of safety properties using SMT model checking techniques. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to software engineering (cs.SE), programming languages (cs.PL), logic (cs.LO), databases (cs.DB), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
